      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a break though. it's like... everything. the exams, the expectations, just being alive and constantly having to perform. it feels like a loop i can't escape. when i say i want it all to be over, i don't mean a nap. i mean i just want the noise to stop forever. it feels like the only real way to get any peace is to just not exist anymore.",
